Niger’s Government Distributing Grain to Famine Victims, Libyan Migrants

-- B y   D j i b r i l   S a i d o u
-- 
2011-07-18T20:43:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-18/niger-s-government-distributing-grain-to-famine-victims-libyan-migrants.html
Niger’s government began
distributing 20,852 tons of grain to 1.4 million victims of
famine and 211,800 migrants who have fled violence in
neighboring  Libya , according to an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  